{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idcdfcad96-7553-11f1-8811-da7bbbed8cd8","identifier":"/us/usc/t47/s616"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"616"},"text":"§ 616.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Internet protocol-based relay services","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Within one year after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2010-10-08"},"text":"October 8, 2010","children":[],"tail":", each interconnected VoIP service provider and each provider of non-interconnected VoIP service shall participate in and contribute to the Telecommunications Relay Services Fund established in section 64.604(c)(5)(iii) of title 47, Code of Federal Regulations, as in effect on "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2010-10-08"},"text":"October 8, 2010","children":[],"tail":", in a manner prescribed by the Commission by regulation to provide for obligations of such providers that are consistent with and comparable to the obligations of other contributors to such Fund."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idcdfcad97-7553-11f1-8811-da7bbbed8cd8"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1934-06-19/ch652"},"text":"June 19, 1934, ch. 652","children":[],"tail":", title VII, § 715, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/260/tI/s103/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–260, title I, § 103(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2010-10-08"},"text":"Oct. 8, 2010","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/124/2755"},"text":"124 Stat. 2755","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
